title: Hunger-Man v1.2.3  for Windows [Pac-Man clone]
description:
Have fun in this arcade style point eater game. The goal is to eat all the points before the timer runs out. To get even more points you will need to turn the 'Worbles' into food, and eat them as many times as you can. Contains 10 Levels!

This game feature an online scoreboard. The game will still run if your offline; however it wont be able to display the scoreboard.



--------------------------------------------------------------------------





Also contains a 30 day trail version of the game engine it was created on that also includes all the resources needed to create your own Pac-Man Like clone.
